ActFisheries Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Ontario Fishery Regulations, 2007
PrecisRegulations Amending the ONTARIO FISHERY REGULATIONS, 2007 in order to correct and clarify errors and definitions, and to make minor changes to the Regulations, which can negatively impact the Province’s ability to enforce fishing rules and to facilitate recreational fishers’ ability to make use of the resources.
